  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">In her letter to Maria Weston Chapman, Deborah Weston said: &quot;I write to commend to Henry&apos;s &amp; your kindness &amp; hospitality my friend John F. Emerson.&quot; Deborah expresses her gratitude to Henry G. Chapman for newspapers he sent to her. She sends a newspaper in return. She comments on Alanson St. Clair&apos;s claim that the pamphlet, &quot;Right and Wrong,&quot; contains an error.</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Attached to page 1 of the manuscript, is a clipping about Edmund Quincy and N.P. Roger.</subfield>
